title: Blazing 5 - Week 14
itunes:title: Blazing 5 - Week 14
description:
Colin goes over his Blazing 5 picks with RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree or disagree with. Here are the games Colin and RJ go over in week 14:


Ravens @ Bills

Broncos @ Texans

Steelers @ Cardinals

Chiefs @ Patriots

Bengals @ Browns


Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick exclusive to this podcast.
